<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1368117" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/glasses.jpg" alt="" width="1000" height="490" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/glasses.jpg 1000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/glasses-360x176.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/glasses-768x376.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" /></p>
<p>动点科技消息，Bose 在国内发布了两款新智能音频眼镜，定价 1999 元。两款产品都采用了动态音质均衡技术，低音细节不会因调低音量而受损；声音澎湃时，也不必担心音乐会因此失真。</p>
<p>其中，「运动款」采用了耐用轻便的塑胶钛（TR90）材质，两侧镜腿嵌入了 22 毫米的全音域发声单元，达到即使在每小时 40 公里的速度下骑行，听觉体验「也同样优异」。</p>
<p>「猫眼款」则更合适日常佩戴，拥有防摔、防刮擦等特质，官方称其低音表现出「更加扣人心弦的震撼效果」。</p>
<p>除此以外，Bose 还推出了消噪耳塞 &amp;无线耳塞、首款消噪电竞耳机和新一代睡眠耳塞。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1368025" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/H1asufjWZJRrO0DI.jpg" alt="" width="3000" height="2000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/H1asufjWZJRrO0DI.jpg 3000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/H1asufjWZJRrO0DI-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/H1asufjWZJRrO0DI-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/H1asufjWZJRrO0DI-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 3000px) 100vw, 3000px" /></p>
<p>其中，消噪耳塞具有 11 级可控消噪等级、全音域出色音质、新鲨鱼鳍舒适耳套、IPX4 防水等级、18 小时续航能力，售价 2299 元，新一代 Bose 无线耳塞售价 1399 元，两者均于 9 月 23 日预售，10 月 15 日开售。</p>
<h3><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1293889" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/dagongs.png" alt="" width="1029" height="180" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/dagongs.png 1029w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/dagongs-360x63.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/dagongs-768x134.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/dagongs-1024x179.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1029px) 100vw, 1029px" /></h3>
<h4><a href="https://www.theverge.com/2020/9/23/21453017/amazon-climate-pledge-friendly-environmental-carbon-footprint-certification">亚马逊推出「气候友好」标签，帮助用户挑选可持续发展产品</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1368118" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/climate-pledge-friendly-1.png" alt="" width="1400" height="1086" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/climate-pledge-friendly-1.png 1400w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/climate-pledge-friendly-1-360x279.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/climate-pledge-friendly-1-768x596.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/climate-pledge-friendly-1-1024x794.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1400px) 100vw, 1400px" /></p>
