<p>该系列以环保型麦秸纤维代替 35％ 的塑料，以由 98％ 回收塑料瓶制成的再生聚酯纤维取代金属格栅。</p>
<h3><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1293890" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo.png" alt="" width="1029" height="180" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo.png 1029w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo-360x63.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo-768x134.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo-1024x179.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1029px) 100vw, 1029px" /></h3>
<h4>大连烂尾 8 年小区业主住进毛坯房</h4>
<p>近日，辽宁大连开发区君临天下业主反映称小区烂尾八年不交房，许多业主迫于生活压力，已经搬进毛坯房。</p>
<p>小区一共涉及 6 栋楼，大约 800 户居民，目前已经有 20 多户搬了 进来，涉事开发商已破产，政府相关部门答复称正在走法律程序。业主贾女士称，目前只希望能给通上水电，满足基本生活。目前，相关部门均未对此做出回应。</p>
<p>网友：「住建局让找管委会，管委会又踢给住建局，让人无语。」「真的有点心疼他们，都是辛苦一辈子的钱买的房，居然遇见这种事。不敢想象有一天我遇见，我应该会崩溃。」</p>
<h3><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1357582" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/thur.png" alt="" width="1029" height="153" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/thur.png 1029w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/thur-360x54.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/thur-768x114.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/thur-1024x152.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1029px) 100vw, 1029px" /></h3>
<h4><a href="https://www.archdaily.com/947598/church-of-beatified-restituta-atelier-stepan?ad_source=search&amp;ad_medium=search_result_all">Church of Beatified Restituta @ 布尔诺 ·捷克</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1368133" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Stepan_Marek_Kostel_Lesna_02.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1333" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Stepan_Marek_Kostel_Lesna_02.jpg 2000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Stepan_Marek_Kostel_Lesna_02-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Stepan_Marek_Kostel_Lesna_02-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Stepan_Marek_Kostel_Lesna_02-1024x682.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p>
<p>关于这个教堂的设计，建筑师 Marek Jan Štěpán 从 1968 年就已经开始酝酿，今年，这座用于纪念修女 Marie Restituta 的教堂终于落成。</p>
<p>其中，建筑主体的一部分是一座圆形的教堂。在教堂顶部，建筑师打造了一圈彩色玻璃窗。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1368134" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Stepan_Marek_Kostel_Lesna_03.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="3000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Stepan_Marek_Kostel_Lesna_03.jpg 2000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Stepan_Marek_Kostel_Lesna_03-360x540.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Stepan_Marek_Kostel_Lesna_03-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Stepan_Marek_Kostel_Lesna_03-683x1024.jpg 683w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p>
<p>当日光穿过彩色玻璃，能为教堂内带来间接光源，不会投下明显的影子，应和教堂整体圆柔温和的感觉。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1368135" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Stepan_Marek_Kostel_Lesna_22.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1333" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Stepan_Marek_Kostel_Lesna_22.jpg 2000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Stepan_Marek_Kostel_Lesna_22-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Stepan_Marek_Kostel_Lesna_22-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Stepan_Marek_Kostel_Lesna_22-1024x682.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1368136" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Stepan_Marek_Kostel_Lesna_23.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1333" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Stepan_Marek_Kostel_Lesna_23.jpg 2000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Stepan_Marek_Kostel_Lesna_23-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Stepan_Marek_Kostel_Lesna_23-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Stepan_Marek_Kostel_Lesna_23-1024x682.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p>
<p>除此以外，教堂本身的圆形设计也象征着「天堂和永恒」；它旁边的方形建筑则寓意着「人间和短暂」。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1368137" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Stepan_Marek_Kostel_Lesna_16.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1333" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Stepan_Marek_Kostel_Lesna_16.jpg 2000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Stepan_Marek_Kostel_Lesna_16-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Stepan_Marek_Kostel_Lesna_16-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Stepan_Marek_Kostel_Lesna_16-1024x682.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p>